| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3922 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ca5d3c92-e278-50eb-8f68-46d586ccfa80"
